{"tid":1209794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 小心駕駛","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T13:04:09.000Z","uid":17550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cecc1ba06cebd36a621b90f29dca18c640f19382","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"香港交通雖然好方便但地鐵三五時就又壞又嚴重延遲咁<br />\n有時候都會忍唔住揸下車返工出入<br />\n揸得車既記得小心駕駛遵守交通規則<br />\n<br />\n- 首先揸開車都知行人、前車基本上係大晒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得要好好留心路面情況，同前車保持適當安全距離<br />\n- 留意交通燈，千祈唔好衝燈。去到燈口收一收，睇清楚轉燈未，黃燈就千祈唔好衝，紅燈就唔使講啦<br />\n小心留意唔好重brake，預留剎車距離；開車前留意好前後左右<br />\n- 轉線記得打燈，等其他道路使用者知道收油讓線<br />\n- 響鞍唔好亂咁用。塞車話唔定係有原因，無謂騷擾其他人<br />\n- 見到緊急車輛，例如救傷車消防車，記得駛開一邊讓路；如果同前後車有預留足夠距離，一定可以駛埋一邊讓路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 保持安全車速，千祈唔好超速；但高速公路都唔可以隨便停車，都要留意有地方有最低車速限制<br />\n- 如果架車有咩頭暈身㷫，駛慢少少，安全第一；真係頂唔順要行得好慢既，打死火燈等後車知，等人地趕時間既可以知道爬頭。當然必要時就停低架車check一check啦<br />\n- 大部分車主都係愛車之人，唔使想捱花撞傷。但意外既野話唔埋，發生意外最緊要保持冷靜，唔好急。報警、影相、保報險... 自己take time去做<br />\n- 棍仔車就小心啲一腳踩到底做一二一二，死火真係好鬼麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過人人技術唔同話唔埋，小心前車後車啦<br />\n<br />\n諗到再同大家分享<br />\n希望大家路上小心，安全到達目的地。凡事忍讓。香港人多車多，要花幾多時間都話唔埋。最緊要人無事丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ca07be09f04392b47526f9192812d7fedc7cbe","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d78a862fbc25f0bf8d1da8c07cfa7b7f0dd2ee","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa15b9fe01b6b2c6e7691d0c6f482be50a8e107","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31297010730f1d538018f81bb457d9e1b1ad727d","tid":1209794,"uid":257527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:33:52.000Z","msg":"嗱，你地唔好搞啲交通燈呀，啲燈壞左、著唔到、俾野遮住左、或者油黑左，又要搵啲警力黎指揮架喇。<br />\n<br />\n#好市民"},{"pid":"a08ea3eaf01c813d8644851e9fdec90ef311b528","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e8459f3f6b1e23a364545a24b18f5984dfdb5b","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:43:04.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e376765c61bd0c7d92f3e9faad4c3db9f382de23","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44e208b18646ae4ef3976bf28321d1f3dbea2a2","tid":1209794,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb439ba2ca74b1fd4ddd05ec76287be050c1149","tid":1209794,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}